    title: 'Receives Facade Damage Photos',
    text: "Main contractors and facilities managers WhatsApp photos of cracked panels, dislodged fixings, storm-damaged composite sheets, and delaminating timber boards. The AI responds instantly, asks about the panel system and building height, and attaches every photo to your repair lead."
  },
  {
    icon: '📸',
    title: 'Wins Subcontract Cladding Slots',
    text: "Main contractors WhatsApp cladding requirements mid-programme — 'SFS is up, need your cladding gang week after next, 400 sqm south elevation.' The first cladding firm to confirm takes the booking."
  },
  {
    icon: '⚡',
    title: 'Captures Architect Material Queries',
    text: "Architects WhatsApp material samples, detail sketches, and specification questions — 'can you match this zinc profile on a curved soffit?' The AI captures the material, detail type, and project context while you fix panels from the MEWP."
  },
  {
    icon: '🌙',
    title: 'Active After Installation Hours',
